&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Performance Marketing Manager is responsible for the strategy, execution, optimization, and reporting of paid media programs that drive growth across KEEN&#39;s marketplace and digital direct businesses, with heavy focus on Amazon Marketplace management. This role manages channel performance, agency partners, and external vendors, translating data into actionable decisions that meaningfully improve efficiency and revenue outcomes. Reporting to the Sr. Acquisition Marketing Manager, this position works closely with KEEN&#39;s Direct to Consumer and PurePlay Sales teams to advance marketplace and digital direct growth through expert, data driven advertising execution. As KEEN&#39;s digital presence evolves, this role will expand its scope into additional performance channels supporting search presence and discoverability.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Essential Functions&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Description&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Campaign Management &amp;amp; Optimization&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Owns and evolves performance marketing execution ensuring alignment to business objectives, budget targets, and growth goals. Drives continuous optimization to improve efficiency, scalability, and return on investment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leads performance analysis and reporting, delivering clear, actionable insights through recurring presentations and deep-dive analyses. Translates complex data into strategic recommendations for cross-functional stakeholders and leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partners cross-functionally across DTC and marketplace businesses to align performance marketing initiatives with brand strategy, demand planning, merchandising, and onsite experience, ensuring cohesive execution across channels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverages and optimizes marketing technology and SaaS platforms to improve campaign performance, measurement accuracy, and operational efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contributes to and influences best practices across global teams, providing guidance on strategy, execution standards, and performance optimization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Agency &amp;amp; Vendor Management&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the day-to-day point of contact for external agency partners and vendors supporting paid media execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set clear performance expectations, manage deliverables, and hold partners accountable to results.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate agency output critically and provide strategic direction to ensure alignment with KEEN&#39;s goals and standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reporting &amp;amp; Performance Analysis&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own reporting on key performance indicators including impressions, clicks, CTR, CPC, conversion rate, ROAS, ACOS, TACOS, and attributed revenue.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and deliver performance reports that communicate results, trends, and strategic recommendations to stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively identify performance drivers, risks, and optimization opportunities through ongoing analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Cross-Functional Collaboration&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with the PurePlay Sales team to align advertising efforts with marketplace objectives, inventory considerations, promotional activity, and category priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with DTC, merchandising, and marketing teams to ensure campaign execution supports broader business goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate performance insights and recommendations with clarity and confidence across functions and levels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Channel &amp;amp; Industry Development&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as an internal expert on Amazon Channel, retail media trends, and marketplace best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive testing initiatives and champion ideas that improve campaign perform

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Collaborate with a global, cross-functional product creation team, guiding projects from design and development milestones through commercialization to deliver products that exceed expectations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Review and analyze design packs to ensure readiness for factory deliverables.&lt;/p&gt;
