&lt;p&gt;Investigate and resolve issues in design tech packages prior to hand-off, addressing potential concerns related to construction, materials, fit and wear, or cost.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Identify and communicate opportunities to product teams for enhancing construction, materials, and components to improve functionality, aesthetics, durability, and fit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
