&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;The Senior Director, Data &amp;amp; Analytics is a strategic enterprise leader responsible for shaping KEEN’s&amp;nbsp;data vision and transforming the organization into a truly data-driven and AI-enabled business. This role&amp;nbsp;goes beyond platform ownership. It defines how data and analytics create competitive advantage across&amp;nbsp;merchandising, DTC, wholesale, supply chain, finance, and global operations. The Senior Director will&amp;nbsp;connect strategy to execution — translating business priorities into scalable data capabilities, modern&amp;nbsp;analytics, and intelligent decision frameworks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;As Head of the Analytics Center of Excellence (CoE), this leader will unify technical and functional&amp;nbsp;analytics communities, elevate data literacy, standardize KPIs, and embed analytics into everyday&amp;nbsp;business decision-making. Success in this role requires both deep technology expertise and strong&amp;nbsp;retail/consumer industry knowledge to ensure rapid, practical impact.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Essential Functions&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Description&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Defines and communicates a compelling enterprise data &amp;amp; AI vision that&amp;nbsp;supports KEEN’s commercial strategy, growth ambitions, and long-range&amp;nbsp;planning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Identifies and prioritizes high-impact analytics opportunities across merchandising, DTC, wholesale, supply chain, and finance — ensuring&amp;nbsp;measurable business outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Develops and leads KEEN’s AI data readiness strategy, enabling predictive insights, automation, personalization, and intelligent decision support.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Provides executive-level thought leadership on how analytics can improve margin, inventory productivity, customer engagement, and operational&amp;nbsp;efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Leads enterprise data architecture and platform direction, ensuring scalability, governance, and reliability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Leads and evolves the Analytics Center of Excellence, establishing governance standards, KPI harmonization, intake processes, and enterprise&amp;nbsp;decision rights.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Builds and develops a high-performing team of Data Architects, Data Engineers, and Technical Data Analysts; strengthen the broader analyst&amp;nbsp;community through education and capability building.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Serves as a trusted advisor to executive leadership; communicate progress through business impact metrics, not just technical milestones.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
