&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Master&#39;s Degree in Technology, Analytics, or Business Leadership focus preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Minimum twelve (12) years of progressive experience in data, analytics, or digital transformation leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
