&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Prepares monthly prepaid amortization schedules and Accounts Payable&amp;nbsp;accruals, including supporting documentation and variance review, to&amp;nbsp;support timely and accurate month-end close.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Coordinates with the Global Controller, Assistant Controller, and FP&amp;amp;A team&amp;nbsp;to review month-end financial results, investigate unusual activity, and&amp;nbsp;support completeness and accuracy of financial reporting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Monitors Accounts Payable and assigned accounting activities to promote&amp;nbsp;consistent

